### Get Hello Greeting (Step 1 endpoint, now with virtual threads in Step 11)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/hello

### Get Health Status of Hello Service
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

### Get Actuator Beans list (to verify moneyFormatter bean exists)
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/beans

### Get Actuator ConfigProps (to inspect buildabank.money properties)
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/configprops
